{"tid":1917501,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"深水埗議辦貼「藍絲與狗」告示　30人揮拳腳踢踩場抗議　3人被捕","createTime":"2020-03-09T13:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T13:55:15.000Z","uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6db5eebfb23764d52efbb944f73abe52337cf461","tid":1917501,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:47:12.000Z","msg":"深水埗區議員長沙灣社區發展力量李文浩與公民黨劉家衡，早前在自資租用的議員辦事處張貼寫有「本辦事處不為任何藍絲提供服務，藍絲與狗不得內進」的告示，事件惹起爭議，連日有人上門抗議。今午（9日）再度有30人到辦事處示威，其間示威者與辦事處人員發生爭執拉扯，有人在大門向着辦公室內人士多次揮拳及起腳踢，亦有人拍打玻璃及毁壞閉路電視，事件中2名女議員助理受傷。警方調查後拘捕3名男子，案件列作刑事毀壞及普通襲擊處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/445478/%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E8%AD%B0%E8%BE%A6%E8%B2%BC-%E8%97%8D%E7%B5%B2%E8%88%87%E7%8B%97-%E5%91%8A%E7%A4%BA-30%E4%BA%BA%E6%8F%AE%E6%8B%B3%E8%85%B3%E8%B8%A2%E8%B8%A9%E5%A0%B4%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0-3%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F445478%2F%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259F%2597%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E8%25B2%25BC-%25E8%2597%258D%25E7%25B5%25B2%25E8%2588%2587%25E7%258B%2597-%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%25A4%25BA-30%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258F%25AE%25E6%258B%25B3%25E8%2585%25B3%25E8%25B8%25A2%25E8%25B8%25A9%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%258A%2597%25E8%25AD%25B0-3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dmama&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FM%2FtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=2fd9be54\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/445478/%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E8%AD%B0%E8%BE%A6%E8%B2%BC-%E8%97%8D%E7%B5%B2%E8%88%87%E7%8B%97-%E5%91%8A%E7%A4%BA-30%E4%BA%BA%E6%8F%AE%E6%8B%B3%E8%85%B3%E8%B8%A2%E8%B8%A9%E5%A0%B4%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0-3%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>支持警察嚴正執法<